** ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN with a  5.25% interest rate** Roughly need $48,000 down to assume this loan.
**Active kick out, but still showing the property. Schedule today.**

Welcome to your own private paradise! Nestled on 5 beautiful acres, this property is a perfect blend of country living and modern convenience. As you make your way down the tree-lined driveway, you'll feel the stress of the day melt away. The remodeled home is a true masterpiece, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The cathedral ceilings and exposed wood beams add character and charm, while the new wood look ceramic tile adds a touch of elegance. Step outside and you'll find a 20x30 workshop with full electricity and an attached carport, perfect for the handy person in your life. Raise your own chickens and enjoy fresh eggs every morning, or indulge your green thumb. Conveniently located close to Chisholm Trail Parkway for easy access to downtown Fort Worth. Fantastic location!
